sk.stu.fiit.Main

Class TourDate

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.stu.fiit.Main.TourDate

  • public class TourDate
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores data about the tour date. This class is used in the TourBuyController and EditTourScheduleController. This class is used when a tour date is loaded from the database.
